This is a petition for an election under Armour & Co., 40 NLRB 1332 (1942) and Globe Machine

represents all full-time and regular part-time drivers who are dispatched or managed from the 
Employer’s 1000 Joyce Avenue, Columbus, Ohio facility. Petitioner seeks an Armour-Globe 
election among the mechanic employees who are managed from the Employer’s 1000 Joyce 
Avenue, Columbus, Ohio facility, to be added to the existing unit.
Voting Unit (Unit A):
All full-time and regular part-time mechanic employees employed by the Employer at its 100 Joyce Avenue, Columbus, Ohio facility; excluding all office clerical employees, professional employees, guards and supervisors as defined in the Act, and all other employees.
